44\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":27322,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/01\/ibn-abbas-respond-firawn\/","url_meta":{"origin":22794,"position":1},"title":"Ibn Abbas on Greeting: I would respond to Pharaoh if he greeted me","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 1, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Sa\u2019id ibn Jubayr reported: Ibn Abbas, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cIf Pharaoh had said to me, \u2018May Allah bless you,\u2019 I would have said, \u2018And you too,\u2019 but Pharaoh has already died.\u201d Source: al-Adab al-Mufrad 1098 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0633\u064e\u0639\u0650\u064a\u062f\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u062c\u064f\u0628\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064d \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31969,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/12\/rabiah-tawbah-allah-turns-first\/","url_meta":{"origin":22794,"position":2},"title":"Rabiah on Tawbah: You can only repent if Allah turns to you first","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 12, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Qushayri reported: A man said to Al-Rabiah al-\u2018Adwiyyah, may Allah have mercy on her, \u201cI have committed many sins and acts of disobedience. If I turn to Allah in repentance, will he turn to me?\u201d Al-Rabiah said, \u201cNo, rather only if he turned to you first could you turn to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19656,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/08\/03\/istighfar-unless-you-stop-asking\/","url_meta":{"origin":22794,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Istighfar: Allah forgives you unless you stop asking","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 3, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"'Uqbah ibn 'Amir reported: A man came to the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, and he said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, one of us has committed a sin.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cIt will be written against him.\u201d The man said, \u201cThen he has sought forgiveness and\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38124,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/08\/15\/maruf-joy-to-sinners\/","url_meta":{"origin":22794,"position":4},"title":"Ma\u2019ruf on Mercy: O Allah, bring joy to the sinners who repent","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 15, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibrahim ibn al-Utrush reported: Ma\u2019ruf al-Karkhi, may Allah have mercy on him, was upon the Tigris river and we were with him as we passed by some people in a boat misbehaving, singing and beating the drum. We said to Ma\u2019ruf, \u201cO Abu Mahfuz, do you not see these people\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6580,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/17\/muhammad-prophet-tawbah-rahmah\/","url_meta":{"origin":22794,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Muhammad: Prophet of repentance, Prophet of mercy","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 17, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"\u201cI am Muhammad; I am Ahmad; I am the ender of Prophethood; I am the gatherer on the Day of Resurrection; I am the Prophet of repentance; and I am the Prophet of mercy.\u201d \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0627 \u0645\u064f\u062d\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0651\u062f\u064c \u0648\u064e\u0623\u064e\u062d\u0652\u0645\u064e\u062f\u064f \u0648\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064f\u0642\u064e\u0641\u0650\u0651\u064a \u0648\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0627\u0634\u0650\u0631\u064f \u0648\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u064f\u0651 \u0627\u0644\u062a\u064e\u0651\u0648\u0652\u0628\u064e\u0629\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u064f\u0651 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u064e\u0651\u062d\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0629\u0650","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/22794","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias